AppController::beforeRender detects which menu items should be showed and which is active, base on $this-&gt;params['controller'] and $this-&gt;params['action'] (actually model just returns array of such items :D)</br><br />
Then layout handles menu drawings :D</br></p>
<p>So I don't have navigation stuff in real controllers not its views</p>
