<p>- In your controller methods (index, view...):</p>
<p>$this-&gt;set('pageId', 'page_sample1');</p>
<p>- In your layout (or where your menu resides):</p>
<p>&lt;body id="&lt;? echo $pageId ?&gt;"&gt;</p>
<p>&lt;ul&gt;<br />
     &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#" id="mnuSample1"&gt;Sample 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</br><br />
     &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#" id="mnuSample2"&gt;Sample 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</br><br />
&lt;/ul&gt;</br></p>
<p>- And finally in your CSS:</p>
<p>#page_sample1 #mnuSample1 {  /* styles to apply to active menu (equivalent to .active) }<br />
#page_sample2 #mnuSample2 {  /* styles to apply to active menu (equivalent to .active) }</br></p>
